R, Baciewicz AM, Bronze MS "Isoniazid drug and food interactions." Am J Med Sci 317 (1999): 304-11[8] Uragoda CG, Kottegoda SR "Adverse reactions to isoniazid on ingestion of fish with a high histamine content." Tubercle 58 (1977): 83-9', 1767369485);
